# AIM Admin OS — Full Dashboard Implementation Plan

## Overview

Build a complete, production-grade "AIM Admin OS" admin dashboard inside the existing React/Vite/TailwindCSS frontend. The existing `AdminDashboard.tsx` (291 lines, single page) will be replaced with a **full multi-page layout** with a persistent sidebar, proper routing, and all requested modules.

> **No separate project needed.** The existing stack already has React, TailwindCSS (via shadcn), recharts, and all necessary libraries. We'll build inside it cleanly.

