## Architecture

### New File Structure
```
src/pages/admin/
├── AdminLayout.tsx          ← NEW: Fixed sidebar + topbar shell
├── AdminDashboard.tsx       ← REPLACE: Full overview page
├── orders/
│   ├── OrdersPage.tsx       ← NEW: Orders table + filters
│   └── OrderDetailPage.tsx  ← NEW: Split-layout order detail
├── products/
│   ├── ProductsPage.tsx     ← NEW: Product list + CRUD
│   └── ProductFormPage.tsx  ← NEW: Add/Edit form with tabs
├── customers/
│   └── CustomersPage.tsx    ← NEW: Customers table + detail
├── analytics/
│   └── AnalyticsPage.tsx    ← NEW: Full analytics charts
└── settings/
    └── SettingsPage.tsx     ← NEW: Platform settings

src/components/admin/
├── Sidebar.tsx              ← NEW: Fixed left nav
├── Topbar.tsx               ← NEW: Search + notifications + profile
├── KpiCard.tsx              ← NEW: Reusable KPI card
├── StatusBadge.tsx          ← NEW: Order/product status badge
├── DataTable.tsx            ← NEW: Reusable sortable table
└── ChartCard.tsx            ← NEW: Chart wrapper card
```

### Routing (added to App.tsx)
```
/admin                   → AdminDashboard
/admin/orders            → OrdersPage
/admin/orders/:id        → OrderDetailPage
/admin/products          → ProductsPage
/admin/products/new      → ProductFormPage
/admin/products/:id/edit → ProductFormPage
/admin/customers         → CustomersPage
/admin/analytics         → AnalyticsPage
/admin/settings          → SettingsPage
```
All wrapped in `AdminLayout` (sidebar + topbar) + `ProtectedRoute` (role: admin).

