| `/api/v1/admin-panel/products/` | GET | Paginated product list for admin |
| `/api/v1/admin-panel/customers/` | GET | Buyer-only user list |
| `/api/v1/admin-panel/orders/<id>/action/` | POST | Mark paid/shipped/cancel |

### `services/django/admin.ts` additions
Add `orders()`, `products()`, `customers()`, `orderAction()` calls.

